  "2348730": {
    "name": "Hauntsville",
    "steam_appid": 2348730,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348730/extras/7e399ae28b429271407e7f7eace62211.avif?t=1750952715\" width=616 height=85 /></span>你，一位无名旅者，发现自己被困在西部边境的鬼城中。所有人，包括雇佣的工人和本该驮你翻山的马，都消失不见了。但远处传来的嚎叫声预示着你即将不再孤单。最好检查一下你的枪吧，伙计，因为它是你在这片“诅咒西部”与潜伏于各处的怪物对抗的唯一伙伴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Hauntsville》是一款以美国西部拓荒的鼎盛时期为背景的恐怖生存游戏。除了身上穿的衣服（以及最多三位最可靠的朋友），你一无所有，必须靠耕种土地才能熬过夜晚。建造家园，探索闹鬼的城镇寻找补给，或者尝试利用荒野中的资源生存下来，同时还要躲避来自北美民间传说的可怕生物！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348730/extras/a7bf07f047f6c044d25c6a452cce8c82.poster.avif?t=1750952715\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348730/extras/a7bf07f047f6c044d25c6a452cce8c82.webm?t=1750952715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348730/extras/a7bf07f047f6c044d25c6a452cce8c82.mp4?t=1750952715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348730/extras/e817e0dbb5d1b0f7dc26667cf20314a6.avif?t=1750952715\" width=616 height=85 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>诅咒西部</strong>：在美国西部拓荒时期的偏远村庄中，体验这段美国历史上的重要时期，与黑暗中的生物进行殊死搏斗。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348730/extras/02cdc6fe4f7973fb5d8cf62ed877c9aa.poster.avif?t=1750952715\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348730/extras/02cdc6fe4f7973fb5d8cf62ed877c9aa.webm?t=1750952715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348730/extras/02cdc6fe4f7973fb5d8cf62ed877c9aa.mp4?t=1750952715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>孤胆或结伴</strong>：西部荒野没有可靠的伙伴可不行。无论你是英雄、恶棍还是普通人，《Hauntsville》都能让你和最多三位伙伴体验一段难忘的西部之旅！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>西部生存</strong>：光靠自己，牛仔很难在西部生存下去。用斧头砍伐树木建造房屋。深入矿井开采铁矿，锻造工具。猎取动物来维持生计。或者带上你的枪，冒险进入闹鬼的城镇搜刮物资——如果你够胆的话。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348730/extras/da9c6c5266f25e966f7637906ff57671.poster.avif?t=1750952715\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348730/extras/da9c6c5266f25e966f7637906ff57671.webm?t=1750952715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348730/extras/da9c6c5266f25e966f7637906ff57671.mp4?t=1750952715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>昼夜循环</strong>：太阳升起时，山谷相对平和，你可以相对安全地探索。但是一旦夜幕降临，一切都将改变。野兽潜伏在各个角落，想把你吃干抹净。从黄昏到黎明，能否生存下来，将是一个未知数。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态天气</strong>r：每次外出时，天气都可能会恶化。蓝天白云，晴空万里，顷刻之间就可能变成暴风雨。爬到高处，暴风雪可能会打你个措手不及，或者夜晚的突然降临让你迷失方向，使你暴露在黑暗中潜伏的未知威胁面前。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348730/extras/b89b5df91d95af414fdf5222bc904389.poster.avif?t=1750952715\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348730/extras/b89b5df91d95af414fdf5222bc904389.webm?t=1750952715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348730/extras/b89b5df91d95af414fdf5222bc904389.mp4?t=1750952715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不可预测</strong>:《Hauntsville》依靠这些复杂的动态系统，来确保没有两局游戏是相同的。你永远无法预料，曾经安全的地方下次去会不会变成怪物的巢穴；你刚标记的富矿会不会被泥土或积雪掩埋；或者简单拾个柴火会不会变成惊心动魄的生存之战。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348730/extras/527da138416eb18be97cae762890f2fc.poster.avif?t=1750952715\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348730/extras/527da138416eb18be97cae762890f2fc.webm?t=1750952715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348730/extras/527da138416eb18be97cae762890f2fc.mp4?t=1750952715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>力求真实</strong>：《Hauntsville》的每一个细节都经过了精心考究，从柯尔特左轮和温彻斯特步枪，到符合历史时期的建筑和服饰，再到山谷中徘徊的来自美国西部甚至更广泛地区的传说生物，都力求真实还原。</p></li></ul>",
